snippet.title: Birdie Burglars App Preview
snippet.description:
Available now for iOS (https://apps.apple.com/us/app/birdie-burglars/id1509336732) and Android (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cocoamoss.birdieburglars).
Or play it online at https://cocoamoss.com/birdie-burglars/birdie-burglars.html
=====
Cocoa Moss presents: Birdie Burglars!

Launch meowmies with your slingshot to stop the birdie burglars!

Birdie Burglars was developed by DDRKirby(ISQ) and Kat Jia, under the Cocoa Moss label.  It was originally developed in 72 hours as an entry for round 46 of the Ludum Dare game jam.  The theme was "Keep It Alive".

Soundtrack download: https://ddrkirbyisq.bandcamp.com/album/birdie-burglars-original-soundtrack
